{"tid":1889691,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警又衝出嚟柒","createTime":"2020-02-20T17:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T15:01:01.000Z","uid":69395,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa0e4d5d5ecc3dc05cb05d5e76b2462063020a4","tid":1889691,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:57:22.000Z","msg":"「一名警務人員懷疑<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">感染2019冠狀病毒病</span></strong>」<br />\n「有一名48歲男性警務人員經測試後初步<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對『2019冠狀病毒病病毒』呈陽性反應</span></strong>」<br />\nCOVID-19 (Coronavirus Disease 2019，即2019冠狀病毒病) 同 SARS-CoV-2 (沙士冠狀病毒二型) 都未識分就衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感染同測試呈陽性梗係講緊個致病原(病毒/細菌等等)啦，邊會講個疾病<br />\n好心佢哋唔想講武漢肺炎，扮pro跟世衛都唔好咁柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qyuvmQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qyuvmQ.png&h=b3a08793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世衛命名：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/technical-guidance/naming-the-coronavirus-disease-(covid-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Femergencies%2Fdiseases%2Fnovel-coronavirus-2019%2Ftechnical-guidance%2Fnaming-the-coronavirus-disease-%28covid-2019&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqFxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=b2aed8d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/technical-guidance/naming-the-coronavirus-disease-(covid-2019</a>)-and-the-virus-that-causes-it"},{"pid":"0610efada1a8218078fde990951d7c30c9a694f3","tid":1889691,"uid":202348,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:58:34.000Z","msg":"七哥開了po<br />\n大家請支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警又衝出嚟柒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1889691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1889691</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid